QUICKSTART INSTALL
==================

This is a quick guide to building and installing.

Assumes install in ~/reorder.

See README for installing required 32-bit packages.

Quickstart install - in ~/reorder
=================================

  mkdir ~/reorder
  cd ~/reorder
  git clone https://github.com/ncar/lrose-netcdf
  git clone https://github.com/ncar/lrose-reorder
  cd lrose-netcdf/
  ./build_and_install_netcdf.m32 -x ~/reorder/
  cd ../lrose-reorder
  setenv CFLAGS -I${home}/reorder/include
  setenv LDFLAGS -L${home}/reorder/lib
  ./configure --prefix=${home}/reorder
  make install

Binaries will be in:

  ~/reorder/bin

To run:

  setenv LD_LIBRARY_PATH ~/reorder/lib



